{"tid":1982842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[-0-0]今次真係輸民意喇","createTime":"2020-04-21T12:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T13:41:07.000Z","uid":1089,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4ca094864b5930e2916f299e00346eabe00606e1","tid":1982842,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:20:37.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，比我做一次標題撚咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w775/public/column_images/87584028_2617427658541286_2139902695715110912_o_22.jpg?itok=qQgHW2Me\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw775%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2F87584028_2617427658541286_2139902695715110912_o_22.jpg%3Fitok%3DqQgHW2Me&h=6a9f1548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1072688?fbclid=IwAR0F6XNJNkMJDzdpmkIwlFaGaLhazqPfFWPykOij6eUxIRsZJICW-BuVkN0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1072688%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0F6XNJNkMJDzdpmkIwlFaGaLhazqPfFWPykOij6eUxIRsZJICW-BuVkN0&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=1474cdfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1072688%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0F6XNJNkMJDzdpmkIwlFaGaLhazqPfFWPykOij6eUxIRsZJICW-BuVkN0&h=ba8e91d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1072688?fbclid=IwAR0F6XNJNkMJDzdpmkIwlFaGaLhazqPfFWPykOij6eUxIRsZJICW-BuVkN0</a><br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解搞到一國一制咁個柒婆民意都仲會上升呀？<br />\n就係因為你班仆街唔登記入HKPORI個pool<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多主流媒體都係用佢地既data去做民情報道<br />\n而到今時今日竟然都仲係好多人唔知PORI係咩黎，甚至以為係奶共狗搞既民調<br />\nHKPORI前身就係香港大學民意研究計劃，有一定既公信力係度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/hkpop-panel-signup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fhkpop-panel-signup&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=39f485ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/hkpop-panel-signup</a><br />\n而家link都比埋你地，即刻同我登記，同埋定期check mailbox睇下有冇問卷做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e728ccabb9fdc6c115f5b477d263bcd511b56f","tid":1982842,"uid":244809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"yup,時代革命係廢話"},{"pid":"106c4e87b65c295b941dbfe90de758d897c61971","tid":1982842,"uid":197286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:24:20.000Z","msg":"對唔字大佬 依家馬上做"},{"pid":"07105a43d2d7d2044acf6dc7db4e527e4ef4f239","tid":1982842,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:25:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7c0e5c6d8f0410e0a58de0950309e5b75b087a11","tid":1982842,"uid":55317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"登記左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79718d4894b4e74ebbbaa9aac96e797ce537d2f7","tid":1982842,"uid":342828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:30:40.000Z","msg":"唔怪你，立即登記咗。"},{"pid":"1b4ae7eef191e6e977f31d8d1cbf1dfc238c59f6","tid":1982842,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:37:29.000Z","msg":"唔會刻意推post<br />\n我地唔係要製造民意，而係要展示民意<br />\n總之唔覺意睇到呢個post既就記得登記啦"},{"pid":"751089e39ad5c54f865c6fee24d50949ae6e1464","tid":1982842,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:38:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a42447a1362adf7c79b8db1af64d11d7c43eb5e4","tid":1982842